：枪械的射速应该要么高要么低，否则可控性不好，我们用 ppsh41 、 pps43 、索米、 kp m/44（芬兰 pps）、 M3 做了测试，发现确实如此。射速很低的 M3 、射速很高的 ppsh41 、索米都很好控，射速不高不低的 kp m/44 和 pps 反而不好控。 老王的观点：这个结论不严谨，控制变量法应该每次只改动一个变量、不同射速的不同枪械比较可控性，变量太多了，比如重量同样对可控性影响巨大，上面的这几支冲锋枪，射速、重量都差异巨大，变量太多，所以没法得出「射速应该要么高要么低可控性才好」的结论巴拉巴拉…、 与此同时老王还提到：想要准确研究射速和可控性的关系，应该如何如何设计试验，才能严谨。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed71eb55da1ade9134e8ab830a4dd4c2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/660182044"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/NPrgc/Rgc48EAMaCTEwODk4NTA0NyD37/mzBjAAOBdAD3IJNjYwMTgyMDQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1719976897.663258", "card_id": "Q_600488343", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "年龄比我小，比我晚进公司，曾经一个部门的同事，突然变成自己的领导了，该如何克服自己不平衡的心态？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-64e6dd470c0983cea5305e92dd2ce109_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/600488343"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/NPrgc/Rgc48EAMaCDk1NzIyMzgwILPC9KIGMAA4E0AQcgk2MDA0ODgzNDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1719976897.665076", "card_id": "Q_657832044", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer